quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Usikelelekile loWo eSandleni saKhe kukho uBukumkani, Onamandla ngaphezulu kwezinto zonke"
  67,2,"Yena loWo Wadala ukufa nokuphila ukuze Anivavanye (kucace ukuba) nguwuphi na kuni olungileyo ngezenzo. Yena nguSobunganga, uMxoleli"
  67,3,"Yena lowo Wadala amazulu asixhenxe alekeneyo. Akuboni kungangqinelani endalweni kaSozinceba. Ngoko ke guquka ujonge (esibhakabhakeni), likhona na ithanda olibonayo"
  67,4,Phinda ujonge kwakhona okwesibini. (Oko) kujonga (kwakho) kuya kubuyela kuwe kuthobekile kudiniwe
  67,5,"Inene Sihombise izulu elikufuphi ngezibane (iinkwenkwezi), Senza kananjalo ngazo oko kugityiselwa ngako amashayâtîn (ooSathana), yaye Sibalungiselele isohlwayo seDangatya"
  67,6,"Ke kaloku okwabo bangakholwayo eNkosini yabo sisohlwayo sesiHogo, hayi ukuba libi kwekhaya (labo) lokugqibela"
  67,7,"Xa bejulwa kuso, beva ukubizela kwaso (okoyikisayo) lo gama sibila nokubila"
  67,8,"Siphantsela ukugqabhuka ngumsindo, maxa onke iqela (elithile) liphoswa ngaphakathi kuso, abagcini baso bayababuza: “Akuzanga kufike Mlumkisi na kuni?”"
  67,9,"(Baphendula) bathi bona: “Ewe, uMlumkisi wayefikile kuthi kodwasamphikisathinasathi:“UAllâhakukhontoAyithumele phantsi, nina (baLumkisi) aninto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba sekulahlekeni okukhulu.”"
  67,10,"Kananjalo baya kuthi: “Akwaba sasiphulaphule okanye saqiqa, ngesingabangakho phakathi kwamadlelane eDangatya loMlilo"
  67,11,"Ke kaloku baya kusivuma isono sabo, ngoko ke kude lee ngabahlali baseDangatyeni loMlilo"
  67,12,"Inene abo bayoyikayo iNkosi yabo Engabonwayo, okwabo iya kuba kukuxolelwa nomvuzo omkhulu"
  67,13,"Ke kaloku nokuba ningazifihla iintetho zenu zasekhusini okanye niziveze elubala, Yena nguMazi woko kusezifubeni (zabantu)"
  67,14,"Akamelanga kwazi na loWo Wadalayo? Kananjalo Yena nguSobubele, Onolwazi (lweento zonke)"
  67,15,NguYe Owenza umhlaba waba phantsi kolawulo lwenu ngoko ke hambani phakathi kwamathambeka wawo nidle kwimbonelelo yaKhe ukanti kukuYe apho uvuko lukhoyo
  67,16,"Ingaba niziva nikhuselekile na ukuba Yena loWo Usezulwini Akanakuwenza umhlaba uniginye, uthi kananjalo ngokukhawuleza ujikeleze (nani)?”"
  67,17,Okanye niziva nikhuselekile ekubeni loWo Usezulwini Akanakuthumela isiphango samatye ngokuchasene nani na? Niya kwazi ke okokuba saba (sibi) kanjani na isilumkiso saM
  67,18,Kananjalo sele baphika kakade abo bangaphambili kunabo saba njani ke isiyalo saM
  67,19,"Abaziboni\tna\tiintaka\t(eziphaphazela)\tphezu\tkwabo ngamaphiko avuliweyo (ngaxa limbi) evalekile? Akukho bani uzibambayo (ukuba zibe sesibhakabhakeni) ngaphandle koSozinceba. Inene Yena nguSokubona ngaphezu kweento zonke"
  67,20,Kanti ngubani na onokuba ngumkhosi wenu anincede ngaphandle koSozinceba? Abangakholwayo abakho ntweni ngaphandle kwenkohliso
  67,21,Ingubani khona onokunondla ukuba Ebenokusuka Ayibambe imbonelelo yaKhe (kuni)? Kodwa bona bathe gqolo ngokudelela nokuchasa (inkolo)
  67,22,Ingaba lowo uhamba erhubuluza ngobuso bakhe ukhokeleleke ngcono na kunalowo umi nkqo eNdleleni ethe Tye
  67,23,"Yithi: “NguYe Onivelisileyo, Waninika ukuva nokubona neentliziyo, kuncinane eninombulelo ngako.”"
  67,24,"Yithi: “NguYe Onenze naba baninzi ngokuphindeneyo emhlabeni, yaye kukuYe apho niza kuqokelelwa khona.”"
  67,25,"Ke kaloku bathi: “Sinini na esisi thembiso, ukuba (nina bakholwayo) nithetha inyaniso?”"
  67,26,"Yithi: “Ulwazi (loko) lukuAllâh, mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo.”"
  67,27,"Kodwa ukusibona kwabo sisondela, ubuso babo bangakholwayo, buya kunxunguphala kuze kuthiwe (kubo): “Oko ke koko nanikubiza"
  67,28,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Niyabona phofu ukuba uAllâh Anganditshabalalisa ndawonye nabo bakunye nam okanye Asenzele inceba, ngubani ongabakhusela bona abangakholwayo esohlwayeni esibuhlungu"
  67,29,"Yithi: “NguSolubabalo; thina sikholiwe kuYe, kananjalo kukuYe apho sixhomekeke khona. Kwaye niza kwazi okokuba ngubani na osekulahlekeni okucacileyo.”"
  67,30,"Yithi: “Niyijongile phofu (yona into yokuba): xa amanzi wenu ebenokusuka atshoniswe emhlabeni, ngubani omnye obeza kunizela namanzi ampompozayo"
  68,1,Nûn. (Ndifunga) ngosiba lokubhala nangoko (iingelosi) zikubhalayo
  68,2,"Wena\tngobabalo\tlweNkosi\tyakho\t(Muhammad) akuphambenanga"
  68,3,Inene okwakho ngumvuzo ongekhe usilele
  68,4,"Kananjalo\tinene\twena\t(ungumntu)\toziphethe\tkakuhle kakhulu"
  68,5,"Ngoko ke uza kubona, nabo baza kubona"
  68,6,Okokuba nguwuphi na kuni othwaxwa (nguSathana)
  68,7,"Inene iNkosi yakho yiYo Eyaziyo okokuba ngubani na olahlekileyo eNdleleni yaYo, IkwayiYo Ebaziyo abakhokelelekileyo"
  68,8,Ungawathobeli ke amaxoki
  68,9,"Wona anqwenela ukuba ugobele ngakuwo, kanti ngawo amakagobele (ngakuwe)"
  68,10,Kananjalo ungamthobeli nawuphi na umfungeli ongento yanto
  68,11,Umhlebi ohamba esasaza intlebendwane ngolunya
  68,12,"Umthinteli wokulungileyo, ogabadelayo, ongumoni"
  68,13,"Isikhohlakali, umgqakhwe1, ongumkhohlisi ngaphezulu"
  68,14,Ngenxa yokuba enobutyebi nabantwana
  68,15,"Xa iiVesi zeThu zicengcelezwa kuye, uthi: “Zintsomi zabantu bakudala!”"
  68,16,Siya kumtshisa enyhekeni yena
  68,17,Inene Sibalingile bona njengoko Salinga amahlulelane esitiya xa afungela ukuya kukha iziqhamo zaso ekuseni
  68,18,"Engatsho nokuthi: “(ukuba iNkosi Ivumile).”"
  68,19,Ke kaloku kwafika kuso apho (esitiyeni) isibetho esivela eNkosini yakho (satsha isitiya eso) esalele wona
  68,20,"Ekuseni Yaba ngathi sivuniwe (kwasa simnyama thsuh, sele sitshe salilahle)"
  68,21,Ke kaloku (ukuvuka kwawo amahlulelane lawo esitiya) abizana kwakusa
  68,22,"(Esithi omnye komnye): “Yiya kwakusekusasa ezityalweni zakho xa usiya kukha iziqhamo.”"
  68,23,Aphuma ke ethethela phantsi
  68,24,"(Esithi): “Akuyi kungena kuni nawuphi na umntu olihlwempu namhlanje"
  68,25,"Ahamba ke kusekwangoko ngokuzimisela, ezicingela ukuba anamandla (okuthintela wonke ubani okanye amahlwempu anokuthi athabathe iziqhamo zesitiya sawo)"
  68,26,"Kodwa athi esakusibona athi: “Inene thina siselahlekweni"
  68,27,Ngapha koko sibandezelekile!”
  68,28,"Oyena uthobekileyo kuwo wathi: “Andikhanga nditsho na kuwe ukuba zukisa (uAllâh)?”"
  68,29,"Bathi (omnye komnye): “Uzuko malube kwiNkosi yethu, inene thina sibe singabenzi bobubi.”"
  68,30,Ke kaloku (baqalisa) ukusondelelana begxekana
  68,31,"Bathi: “Yeha kuthi, inene thina sibe ngabagabadeli"
  68,32,"Mhlawumbi iNkosi yethu Iya kusinika into engcono kunaso, inene thina eNkosini yethu singabaneminqweno.”"
  68,33,"Saba njalo ke isohlwayo (seli hlabathi) nesohlwayo selizayo esingaphaya, ukuba bebesazi"
  68,34,"Inene\tokwabenzi\tbokulungileyo\tyiMiyezo\tyolonwabo eseNkosini yabo"
  68,35,Ingaba Siza kuphatha amaMuslim njengezaphula- mthetho na
  68,36,Kwenzeka ntoni na kuni? Kanti lunjani na ugwebo lwenu
  68,37,Okanye mhlawumbi ninesibhalo enifunda sona
  68,38,Eniza kufumana konke enikunqwenelayo (ngaso)
  68,39,"Okanye nineminqophiso (esisibophelelo) kuThi, eqhuba iye kuma kwiMini yoVuko, (ekubonakala) okokuba niya kuba noko nigwebe ukuba nibe kuko"
  68,40,Babuze okokuba nguwuphi na apha kubo oza kukumela ngenene oko
  68,41,Okanye mhlawumbi banamahlulelane? Mabeze namahlulelane abo kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  68,42,"NgeMini ubuqu buka-Allâh buya kutyhileka, ke kaloku baya kubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (kuAllâh) kodwa (abahanahanisi) abayi kukwazi ukukwenza oko"
  68,43,"Amehlo abo aya kuthotyelwa phantsi, bathiwe wambu kukuhlazeka; kaloku babedla ngokubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (emthandazweni) besenempilo entle (ehlabathini)"
  68,44,"Ndiyeke ke Mna (Muhammad Ndiqubisane) nalowo uyiphikayo le ntetho (i’Kur’ân), Thina Siya kumana ukubakhokelela apho bangaziyo"
  68,45,"Yaye Ndiya kubanika ixesha, inene elaM icebo liqinile"
  68,46,Makube mhlawumbi ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo Myalezo) ekucaca okokuba bazifumanisa benetyala elingumthwalo kubo
  68,47,"Okanye mhlawumbi banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  68,48,"Yiba nomonde ke wena ngesigqibo seNkosi yakho, ungabi njengomfo wentlanzi (uYûnus) xa wakhwazayo ekwimo yonxunguphalo"
  68,49,"Ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yenceba eyavela eNkosini yakhe eyamgubungelayo, ngewayejulwe elunxwemeni oluze enokusoleka"
  68,50,Ke kaloku iNkosi yakhe yamkhetha yamenza ilungisa
  68,51,"Inene abo bangakholwayo bebengakwenza utyibilike ngamehlo abo (ngendlela abakujonga ngayo) xa besiva umyalezo kananjalo bathi, “Inene yena ushiywe ziingqondo.”"
  68,52,Kodwa akunto yimbi oku ngaphandle kokuba sisikhumbuzi emazweni
  69,1,INyaniso
  69,2,Yintoni na iNyaniso
  69,3,Yintoni na enokukwazisa ukuba iyintoni na iNyaniso
  69,4,AmaThamûd nama’Ad ayiphika intlekele ebethayo (ukubetha kweYure yoMgwebo)
  69,5,Ke kaloku amaThamûd (lawo) atshatyalaliswa sisithonga esongamelayo
  69,6,"Nama’Ad\t(nawo)\tatshatyalaliswa\tngumoya\tovuthuza ngokutswinayo"
  69,7,"Lowo Yena uAllâh Wawunyanzelayo phezu kwabo ubusuku obusixhenxe neemini ezisibhozo zilandelelana, wawungababona abantu apho bedunduluzile bengathi ngamaphanga ezibhukubhuku zemithi yesundu"
  69,8,Ukhona ombonayo kubo (osaphilayo)
  69,9,Kwaza kweza uFir’awn nabo babengaphambili kunaye abazivuyavuyayo izixeko ngesono
  69,10,"Baya ababathobela abaProfeti beNkosi yabo, Yabahlasela ke ngohlaselo olumandla"
  69,11,"Inene athi amanzi akuphuphuma, Sanithwala nina (ookhokho benu) enqanaweni eyayidada (kaNûh)"
  69,12,Khon’ukuze Siyenze ibe sisikhumbuzi kwanokuba indlebe evayo iphaphame ngayo
  69,13,Xa iXilongo livuthelwa ngesithonga esinye
  69,14,Umhlaba neentaba ziphakanyisiwe zaphinda (zagangathwa) zeetyaba ngesithonga esinye
  69,15,Ngaloo Mini ke isehlo (uVuko) siya kuhla
  69,16,Nezulu liya kucandeka kubini (livuleke) kuba ngayo loo Mini liya kuba yacuyacu libe dlaka-dlaka
  69,17,"Ke kaloku emacaleni alo kuya kuba kukho iingelosi, ezisibhozo ngalooMini ziya kuba zithwele iTrone yeNkosi yakho phezu kwazo"
  69,18,"Ngayo loo Mini niya kuziswa ekugwetyweni, akukho mfihlo yenu iya kufihlakala"
  69,19,"Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sokunene uya kuthi: “Nantsi! Fundani iNcwadi yam"
  69,20,“Inene mna ndaye ndakholwa ukuba ndiza kudibana nokubhaliweyo (ngam)
  69,21,"Lowo ke uya kuba sebomini, obumnandi"
  69,22,Epaladesi ephakamileyo
  69,23,Iziqhamo zona ziya kuba ngezipho eziya kuba sezantsi kufutshane esandleni (sakhe)
  69,24,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yidlani nizanelise ngenxa yoko nazenzela kona (kwangethuba) ngemihla eyadlulayo.”"
  69,25,"Ke lowo uya kunikwa iNcwadi yakhe esandleni sakhe sokhohlo, uya kuthi: “Yeha kum, akwaba bendingayinikwanga iNcwadi yam"
  69,26,Andayazi kwa ukuyazi into ebhalwe ngam
  69,27,Akwaba (ukufa kwam) bekusisiphelo sobomi bam
  69,28,Ubutyebi bam abundincedanga nto
  69,29,Igunya lam limkile kum (nokuhlonipheka kuphelile kum)!2”
  69,30,"(UAllâh Uya kuthi), “Mbambeni nimkhonkxe"
  69,31,Nimqhubele eDangatyeni loMlilo (wesiHogo)
  69,32,"Nimqamangele ngekhonkco\telibude balo\tbuzii kubite ezingamashumi asixhenxe"
  69,33,"Inene yena wayengakholwa kuAllâh, Ongoyena Mkhulu.”"
  69,34,Engazanga akhuthaze nokondliwa kwamahlwempu
  69,35,"Ngoko\tke\takasenaye namhlobo wakhe\tosenyongweni namhlanje"
  69,36,"Engenakutya\tkumbi\tngaphandle\tkwencindi\tephuma ezilondeni (ububomvu)"
  69,37,Akukho nabani na oya kuyitya (loo ncindi) ngaphandle kwaboni
  69,38,Ndifunga ngoko nikubonayo
  69,39,Nangoko ningakuboniyo
  69,40,"(Okokuba),\tinene\t(i’Kur’ân)\tililizwi\tlomthunywa ohloniphekileyo"
  69,41,"Kananjalo ayilolizwi lembongi, kuncinane enikukholelwayo"
  69,42,"Ingelolizwi lomvumisi, kuncinane enikukhumbulayo"
  69,43,(Yona) sisiTyhilelo esivela kwiNkosi yamaphakade
  69,44,Ukanti ukuba ngaba yena (uMuhammad) ebengaqamba iintetho zobuxoki ngaThi
  69,45,Ke kaloku beSiya kumxhakamfula ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  69,46,Size Simqhawule umthambo (wegazi osuka entliziyweni)
  69,47,Kwaye akukho namnye kuni obeya (kuSithintela Thina) kuye
  69,48,Inene yona (i’Kur’ân) isisikhumbuzi kumalungisa
  69,49,"Kananjalo, Siyazi Thina okokuba phakathi kwenu kukho abaphiki"
  69,50,Ke kaloku yona (i’Kur’ân) iya kuba ngunobangela wokuzisola kwabangakholwayo
  69,51,Yona ke ngenene iyinyaniso yokwenene
  69,52,(Wena) zukisa igama leNkosi yakho eNkulu
  70,1,Umbuzi wabuza ngesohlwayo esele siza kuhla
  70,2,Phezu kwabangakholwayo ekungekho bani unokusijika
  70,3,"Sivela kuAllâh, uMnini weendlela ezinyukayo"
  70,4,Iingelosi noMoya (oyiNgcwele) ziya kunyuka ziye kuYe ngeMini ebude bayo bungamawaka angamashumi amahlanu
  70,5,Linda ke ngomonde omhle
  70,6,Inene bona bayibona (ngathi) imgama
  70,7,Kodwa Thina Siyibona ikufuphi
  70,8,NgoMhla isibhakabhaka siya kuba njenge-oli emdaka
  70,9,Iintaba zibe njengoboya
  70,10,Akuyi kubakho mhlobo uya kubuza ngomhlobo (wakhe)
  70,11,Baya kubonana. Umoni uya kunqwenela ukuba akwaba ebeza kuhlawulelwa (akhululwe) esohlwayweni saloo Mini ngabantwana bakhe
  70,12,Nangomkakhe nomntakwabo
  70,13,Nezizalwana zakhe ezizezona zisondeleyo kuye ezamnika indawo yokuhlala
  70,14,Naye wonke osemhlabeni ukuba amsindise
  70,15,Nakanye! Inene iya kuba liDangatya (loMlilo wesiHogo)
  70,16,Oxwantsula (utshise) intlonze (yentloko)
  70,17,Ubize (bonke) abafulathela (inyaniso) balushiya ukholo
  70,18,Baqokelela ubutyebi babufumba
  70,19,Inene umntu wadalwa waxhalaba (wasisingxami)
  70,20,Xa ububi (intsokolo) bumchukumisa akanyamezeli
  70,21,Xa okulungileyo (ubutyebi) kumchukumisa abe nobugogotya (abe ligqolo)
  70,22,Ngaphandle kwabo bazinikeleyo kwiSalâh (emthandazweni)
  70,23,Abo benza iSalah yabo rhoqo
  70,24,"Nabo\tebutyebini\tbabo\tkukho\tamalungelo\tazekayo (kwabasweleyo)"
  70,25,"Kumngqibi ocelayo, nalowo ubandezekileyo, ulahlekelwe yimpahla nobutyebi bakhe"
  70,26,Nabo bakholwayo kwiMini yembuyekezo
  70,27,Nabo banoloyiko lwesohlwayo seNkosi yabo
  70,28,Inene isohlwayo seNkosi yabo seso kungekho namnye ungaziva ekhuselekile kuso
  70,29,Nabo babulondolozayo ubunyulu babo
  70,30,"Ngaphandle kwakubafazi babo nabo babanjwe zizandla zabo zokunene, bona abanakusoleka"
  70,31,"Kodwa ke lowo ufuna okungaphaya kunoku, inene abenza njalo ngabagabadeli"
  70,32,Ke bona abo bagcina intembeko nezithembiso zabo
  70,33,Nabo baqinayo kubungqina babo
  70,34,Nabo bazilondolozayo kakuhle iiSalâh zabo
  70,35,Abo ngabo baya kuba seMiyezweni benentlonipheko
  70,36,"Yintoni kanye ngabo bangakholwayo, bengxama phambi kwakho nje (Muhammad)"
  70,37,"(Bahlale)\tekunene\t(kwakho)\tnasekhohlo\t(kwakho) bengamaqela ahlukeneyo"
  70,38,Ingaba ngamnye kubo ulangazelela ukungena eMyezweni wolonwabo
  70,39,Nakanye! Thina Sibadale ngoko bakwaziyo
  70,40,"Ngoko\tke\tNdifunga\tngeNkosi\tyeempuma\tneentshona okokuba Thina inene Sinamandla"
  70,41,Singabeka abanye abangcono endaweni yabo; yaye akukho nto inokuSithintela Thina
  70,42,Bayeke ke wena bancokole ubuvuvu bazonwabise bade bahlangane neMini yabo abathenjiswe ngayo
  70,43,NgeMini abaya kuphuma ngokungxama emangcwabeni bangxame ngathi baya esithixweni esimisweyo
  70,44,"Amehlo abo ethotyiselwe phantsi, ihlazo liya kuba libambethe. YiMini abathenjiswe ngayo ke leyo"
  71,1,"Inene, Thina Sathumela uNûh kubantu bakubo, (Sisithi): “Lumkisa abantu bakuni phambi kokuba bafikelwe sisohlwayo esibuhlungu.”"
  71,2,"Wathi yena: “Hini na bantu bakuthi! Inene mna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo kuni"
  71,3,"(Ndisithi kuni):‘KhonzaniuAllâh, noyikeYena, nindithobele.’"
  71,4,"Wathi, ‘(UAllâh) Uya kunixolela izono zenu Aze Animele (Ngesohlwayo) ixesha elikhethiweyo. Inene ixesha elikhethwe nguAllâh xa sele lifikile, aliyi kubanjezelwa, ukuba benisazi.’”"
  71,5,"Wathi: “Nkosi yam inene mna ndibamemile abantu bakuthi ubusuku nemini.”"
  71,6,Kodwa ukubamema kwam akubenzelanga nto ngaphandle (kokubongezelela) ukubaleka (enyanisweni)
  71,7,"Kananjalo maxa onke ndibamema (ndisithi kubo) Uya kuba xolela Wena, (Basuka) bafake iminwe yabo ezindlebeni zabo, bazigqume ngeengubo zabo bale bakhukhumale ngenkukhumalo (enkulu)"
  71,8,Ndibamemile esidlangalaleni
  71,9,"Ndaphinda ndenza isibhengezo, (ndathetha) nabo ekhusini"
  71,10,"Ndisithi (kubo): “Celani itarhu eNkosini yenu. Inene Yona, nguMxoleli wanaphakade"
  71,11,Yona Iya kunithumelela (imvula) esibhakabhakeni ingumkhumezelo
  71,12,"Iya kunandisela ubutyebi nabantwana, Ininike izitiya, nemilambo.”"
  71,13,"Yintoni na ngani le nto ningamoyikiyo uAllâh, ningenalo nethemba lomvuzo (ovela kuYe)"
  71,14,Lo gama Yena Wanidala ngokwamanqanaba ahlukeneyo
  71,15,"Aniboni na ukuba uAllâh Wawadala kanjani na amazulu asixhenxe, elinye phezu kwelinye"
  71,16,"Wenza inyanga yaba kukukhanya apho, ilanga lona laba sisibane"
  71,17,UAllâh Wanikhupha eluthulini lomhlaba
  71,18,Emva kwethuba Uza kunibuyisela kwakuwo (umhlaba lowo) Aphinde Anibuyise kwakhona (ngeMini yoVuko)
  71,19,Kananjalo uAllâh Unenzele umhlaba waphangalala
  71,20,Khona ukuze nihambe apho kuwo ezindleleni ezivulekileyo
  71,21,"UNûh wathi: “Nkosi yam baye abandithobela mna, balandela lowo ubutyebi bakhe nabantwana bakhe bungamongezeleli nto ngaphandle kwelahleko"
  71,22,Kananjalo bona baqulunqe iyelenqe elikhulu
  71,23,"Bathi: “Ningabashiyi oothixo benu; ningamshiyi uWadd, uSuwâ, uYagrhûth uYa-’û’k noNasr"
  71,24,Kananjalo balahlekise abaninzi. Ke kaloku (Wena Allâh) ‘Ungabandiseli nto abenzi bobubi ngaphandle kokulahleka”’
  71,25,Ngenxa yezono zabo baye batshoniswa emanzini baza bangeniswa eMlilweni. Abazanga bafumana mncedi wumbi endaweni ka-Allâh
  71,26,"Ke kaloku uNûh wathi: “Nkosi yam Ungashiyi namnye kwabangakholwayo phezu komhlaba"
  71,27,"Ukuba Ubashiyile, baya kulahlekisa izicaka zaKho yaye abayi kuzala nto ngaphandle kwezingcoli (ezinoburheletya), ezingakholwayo"
  71,28,Nkosi yam! Ndixolele mna nabazali bam nongena endlwini yamelikholwanamakholwanamakholwakazionke. Kekaloku kubenzi bobubi ungongezi nto ngaphandle kwentshabalalo.”
  72,1,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Kuye kwatyhilwa kum okokuba iqela leejinni1 liye laphulaphula (ucengcelezo lwe’Kur’ân), lathi; “Inene thina sive i’Kur’ân engummangaliso"
  72,2,"Ikhokelela eNdleleni elungileyo, kananjalo sikholiwe thina kuyo yaye asisayi kwayamanisa namnye eNkosini yethu"
  72,3,Kananjalo (yona ifundisa okokuba) Osenyangweni ngoYena UyiNkosi yethu Ehloniphekileyo; Yena Akathabathanga mfazi nanyana
  72,4,Ke kaloku osisidenge phakathi kwethu (uSathana) ebekade ethetha ugabadelo olubi ngoAllâh
  72,5,Ukanti thina besihleli sicinga okokuba abantu neejinni azimelanga kuthetha buxoki ngoAllâh
  72,6,"Kananjalo bekukade kukho ebantwini abo bafuna ukhuseleko kwiiJinni, zona ke zabongezelela ubudenge kuphela"
  72,7,Nazo bezicinga kanye njengoko benicinga zisithi uAllâh Akanakuze Athumele bani (ukuba abe nguMthunywa)
  72,8,Kananjalo thina sazama ukuya ezulwini kodwa sasuka salifumana lizeliswe ngabalindi abanamandla namadangatya avuthayo
  72,9,Ke kaloku thina sasidla ngokuncathama kwimimandla yezulu ukuya (kubisa) siphulaphule kodwa ophulaphulayo ngoku uya kufumana idangatya lomlilo limlalele
  72,10,"Kananjalo asazi nokuba kokungcolileyo na oko kuza kuhlela abo basemhlabeni, singazi nokuba iNkosi yabo Isingisele ekubabekeni eNdleleni elungileyo na"
  72,11,"Bakhona abangamalungisa phakathi kwethu, babe abanye bengenjalo, singamaqela aneendlela ezahlukeneyo"
  72,12,"Kananjalo sicinga ukuba asinako ukusiphepha isohlwayo sika-Allâh emhlabeni, singekhe siMphephe nangokubhabha"
  72,13,Ke kaloku thina ukusiva kwethu isikhokelo siye sakholwa kuso. Ke kaloku lowo ukholwa eNkosini yakhe akayi kuba naloyiko lwasinciphiso somvuzo wezenzo zakhe ezilungileyo okanye ukongezelelwa kwesohlwayo sezono zakhe
  72,14,"Kananjalo phakathi kwethu kukho abangamaMuslim kuze phakathi kwethu kubekho ama’kâsit (abangakholwayo), abo bamkele i-Islam, abanjalo bazifumanele iNdlela elungileyo.”"
  72,15,Ke wona ama’kâsit aya kuba ziinkuni zesiHogo
  72,16,"Ukuba ngaba bona (abangakholwayo) bebenokukholwa kuAllâh, bahambe eNdleleni elungileyo, beSiza kubapha indyebo yamanzi (imvula)"
  72,17,"Ukuze Sibalinge ngawo. Ngoko ke lowo ukreqayo kwinkumbulo yeNkosi yakhe [i’Kur’ân, (iNkosi yakhe)] Iya kumenza angene kwisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  72,18,"Kananjalo Yona (Ityhile) okokuba iimasjid zezika-Allah, ngoko ke musani ukunqula wumbi (kuzo)"
  72,19,"Ke kaloku ukuphakama kwesiCaka sika-Allâh (uMuhammad) sinqula iNkosi yaso emthandazweni, zona (iijinni) zenza isangqa ziyinyambalala zingathi enye ikhwele phezu kwenye (ukuza kuphulaphula)"
  72,20,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndinqula iNkosi yam (kuphela) yaye andayamanisi mahlulelane kuYo.”"
  72,21,"Yithi: “Akukho phantsi kwagunya lam ukuba nihlelwe bu bubi, okanye ukuningenisa eNdleleni elungileyo.”"
  72,22,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Akukho namnye ongandikhusela kwisohlwayo sika-Allâh, ndingeze ndifumane lukhuseleko ngaphandle kwakuYe"
  72,23,"Okwam kukuvakalisa okuvela kuAllâh nomyalezo waKhe. Nabani na lowo ungaMthobeliyo uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, inene okwakhe lowo nguMlilo wesiHogo, uya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade.”"
  72,24,"(Abayi kukholwa) de babone oko babethenjiswe ngako, baya kwazi ngoko ke ukuba ngubani na kanye ekungekho yakhe ngokubhekiselele kubancedisi, noyena ungento yanto mayela nenani (labancedisi)"
  72,25,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna andazi nokuba oko nithenjiswe ngako sele kukufuphi na nokuba iNkosi yam Iya kukubekela ixesha elide kusini na"
  72,26,Yena Yedwa (uAllâh) nguSolwazi wokungabonwayo kwaye Akakubonisi nabani na okungabonwayo kwaKhe.”
  72,27,"Ngaphandle kwalowo Athande (ukumbonisa) kubaThunywa baKhe, Inene Yena Uthumela phambi kwakhe (umthunywa lowo waKhe) nasemva kwakhe abakhi-mkhanyo"
  72,28,"(Yena uAllâh) Uyabakhusela (abaThunywa baKhe) Ade Abone okokuba bona (abaThunywa) bayivakalisile imiyalezo yeNkosi yabo (uAllâh), kwanokuba Yena Ugubungele konke oko kukunye nabo kwaye Yena (uAllâh) Ubala izinto zonke"
  73,1,Hini na wena uzisongele (ngeengubo)
  73,2,"Vuka (uthandaze) ebusuku, nokuba kukancinane"
  73,3,Isiqingatha sabo ubusuku okanye unciphise nokuba yintwana kuso
  73,4,"Okanye uyongeze, ucengceleze i’Kur’ân ngocengcelezo olulinganiselweyo"
  73,5,Inene Thina Siya kuphosa phezu kwakho ilizwi elinzima
  73,6,Inene iiyure zobusuku zizona zinemvakalo (entliziyweni naselwimini) yaye zilunge ngakumbi emazwini
  73,7,Inene okwakho ebudeni bemini kukuxakeka (okuthabatha ithuba) elide
  73,8,"Khumbula\tigama\tleNkosi\tyakho,\tuzinikele\tkuYo ngokuzinikela okupheleleyo"
  73,9,"(Yena uAllâh) YiNkosi yeMpuma neNtshona; akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe, wena zithabathele Yena ukuba Abe nguMpumelelisi wemicimbi (yakho)"
  73,10,"Yiba nomonde nangoko bakutshoyo (ngawe), ungabahoyi kananjalo wena ngokungahoyi okuyindlela elungileyo"
  73,11,"Ubayekele kuM abaphiki, abo bahamba lula (ebomini), bamele okwethutyana"
  73,12,Inene kuThi kukho amakhamandela (okubabopha) noMlilo ovuthayo
  73,13,"Nokutya\tokukrwitshayo\t(okomayo).\tNesohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  73,14,NgeMini umhlaba neentaba ziya kungcangcazela zize iintaba zibe yinduli yentlabathi echithakala phantsi
  73,15,"Inene Thina Sithumele uMthunywa kuni (bantu), olingqina phezu kwenu njengoko Sasithumele uMthunywa kuFir’awn"
  73,16,"Kodwa yena uFir’awn akazanga amthobele uMthunywa, Samhlasela ke ngohlaselo olutshabalalisayo"
  73,17,"Ningayoyika njani ningakholwa nakukholwa kuyo, iMini leyo iya kwenza abantwana babe nezimvi"
  73,18,Izulu liya kuqhekeka lahlukane ngayo (loo Mini) kwaye esaKhe (uAllâh) isithembiso siyazaliseka
  73,19,"Inene le yinkumbuzo, lowo uthandayo makathabathe iNdlela eya eNkosini yakhe"
  73,20,"INkosi yakho Iyakwazi (Muhammad) ukuba uyaphakama (uthandaze) phantse izahlulo ezibini kwezithathu zobusuku okanye isiqingatha sabo, okanye isithathu sabo, Lenza njalo ke neqela labo bakunye nawe. Ke kaloku uAllâh Uyabazi (ubude) bobusuku nobemini. Uyazile Yena into yokokuba nina (maMuslim) aninakukwazi ukwenza njalo, Waza Wabuyela kuni ngenceba, ngoko ke cengcelezani okulula (kuni) kwe’Kur’ân. Uyazile nento yokuba kuza kuye kubekho abanye abagulayo phakathi kwenu, abanye babeseluhambeni emhlabeni befuna okuvela kwiziBele zika- Allâh, abanye (benu) besilwa eNdleleni ka-Allâh. Ngoko ke nina cengcelezani okulula kuyo, nenze iSalâh ninikele ngeZakâh, niboleke uAllâh imboleko entle. Ke kaloku nantoni na elungileyo eniza nayo ngaphambili ngokwenu, niya kuyifumana kuAllâh. Iya kuba ngcono ibe nkulu ngokomvuzo. Celani itarhu kuAllâh Inene uAllâh Uyaxolela, Unenceba"
  74,1,Hini na wena uzithe wambu ngeengubo
  74,2,Vuka ulumkise
  74,3,INkosi yakho (uAllâh) Yenze nkulu
  74,4,Iimpahla zakho uzicoce
  74,5,Ubumdaka ubuphephe (unqulo lwezithixo)
  74,6,Ungenzi inceba ufune engaphezulu (kunayo) wena
  74,7,Kodwa mayela neNkosi yakho yiba nomonde
  74,8,Ke kaloku lakuvuthelwa iXilongo
  74,9,Loo Mini iya kuba yiMini enzima
  74,10,Kwabangakholwayo ayiyi kuba lula
  74,11,Ndiyeke ke Mna nalowo Ndamdala NdiNdedwa
  74,12,Ndampha imfumba yobutyebi
  74,13,Nabantwana bekhona (kuye)
  74,14,"Ndandlala (into yonke) phambi kwakhe, Ndimenzela lula ubomi bakhe"
  74,15,Kanti usanqwenela ukuba Ndimongezelele ezinye
  74,16,Nakanye! Inene yena uye waba nendelelo mayela neeVesi zeThu
  74,17,Mna Ndiya kumgubungela ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu
  74,18,Inene yena wacinga waqulunqa
  74,19,Makaqalekiswe ke ngendlela awaqulunqa ngayo
  74,20,Kwakhona makaqalekiswe ngendlela awaqulunqa ngayo
  74,21,Waphinda wacinga kwakhona
  74,22,Wafingi’iintshiya wakhangeleka enomsindo
  74,23,Wabuya umva ekhukhumele
  74,24,"Wathi: “Le (‘Kur’ân) asinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba ngumlingo obonelwe kubantu bakudala"
  74,25,Le asinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba lilizwi lomntu!”
  74,26,Mna ke Ndiya kumqhubela eSa’kar1 (eMlilweni wesiHogo)
  74,27,Yintoni na engakwenza wazi ukuba iyintoni na iSa’kar
  74,28,"Ayishiyi nto kuyo, ingashiyi nto (ingayitshisanga)"
  74,29,Ijika (yenze mnyama) izikhumba
  74,30,Phezu kwayo (iSa’kar) lishumi elinethoba (leengelosi)
  74,31,"Ke kaloku Asibenzanga abalindi boMlilo (wesiHogo) baba yinto yimbi ngaphandle kweengelosi. Kananjalo Asilenzanga layinto yimbi inani lazo ngaphandle kokuba libe luvavanyo lwabo bangakholwayo kwanokuba abo babenikwe isiBhalo baqonde baneliseke kwanokuba abo bakholwayo bande elukholweni nabo babenikwe isiBhalo namakholwa bangabi nakuthandabuza kwanokuba abo bantliziyo zabo zinesifo (abahanahanisi) nabangakholwayo bathi: “Uthetha ukuthini na uAllâh ngawo lo mzekelo?” Ngolo hlobo ke uAllâh Ulahlekisa lowo Athande ukumlahlekisa Akhokele lowo Athande ukumkhokela. Ukanti akukho namnye owaziyo amajoni eNkosi yakho ngaphadle kwaYo. Ke kaloku (ukukhankanywa koMlilo) akunto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba yinkumbuzo ebabantwini"
  74,32,Nakanye! (Ndifunga) ngenyanga
  74,33,Nangobusuku xa busimka
  74,34,Nangentseni xa iba mhlophe
  74,35,"Inene wona [uMlilo (yintuthumbiso)] enkulu"
  74,36,Unjengesilumkiso kubantu
  74,37,Khona ukuze lowo uthandayo phakathi kwenu aqhubeke (nokukholwa) okanye ahlale phantsi (engakholwa)
  74,38,Wonkeumphefumlouyakubanjwangaloontouyisebenzeleyo
  74,39,Ngaphandle kwamadlelane okunene
  74,40,"Aya kuba seMiyezweni, ebuzana"
  74,41,Ngabaphuli-mthetho
  74,42,"(Ebabuza okokuba): Yintoni na enifake eSa’kar?”"
  74,43,"Baya kuthi bona: “Sasingengabo abanye babo babethandaza"
  74,44,Sasingondli namahlwempu
  74,45,"Kananjalo\tsasidla\tngokuthetha\tamampunge\t(ngabo babethandaza)"
  74,46,Kwaye sasidla ngokuyiphika iMini yembuyekezo
  74,47,“Sada safikelwa kukufa okwakungathandabuzeki.”
  74,48,Ngoko ke ayiyi kubanceda nto intethelelo yabo nabaphi na abathetheleli
  74,49,Yintoni kanye ngabo le nto bayitshikilelayo inkumbuzo
  74,50,Babe ngathi ziimbongolo zasendle ezothukileyo
  74,51,Ezibaleka ingonyama
  74,52,Ukusuka apho umntu ngamnye kubo unqwenela ukuba anikwe isiBhalo esele sandlaliwe
  74,53,Nakanye! Kodwa bona abanaloyiko loBomi oBuzayo
  74,54,Nakanye! Inene yona (i’Kur’ân) yinkumbuzo
  74,55,Ke kaloku lowo ufunayo uya kuyikhumbula
  74,56,"Kananjalo abayi kukhumbula nto ngaphandle koko uAllâh Athande ukuba bakukhumbule. Yena Ufanelwe kukoyikwa, Wanele ukuba Axolele"
  75,1,Ndifunga ngeMini yoVuko
  75,2,Nangomphefumlo okhalimayo
  75,3,Ingaba umntu (lo) ucinga ukuba Asiyi kuwadibanisa na amathambo akhe
  75,4,Ewe nje Siyakwazi Thina nokumisa ngendlela iintupha zeminwe yakhe
  75,5,Kodwa umntu unqwenela ukuqhubekela phambili nokwenza isono
  75,6,"(Ude) abuze: “Inini na iMini YoVuko?”"
  75,7,Ke kaloku xa ukubona2 (kwabo) kuphandliwe
  75,8,Nenyanga iba mnyama
  75,9,Ilanga nenyanga zidityanisiwe
  75,10,"Umntu uya kuthi ngalooMini: “Iphi na indawo yokubalekela?”"
  75,11,Nakanye! Akuyi kubakho ndawo yakhuseleko
  75,12,ENkosini yakho ngaloo Mini kuya kubakho (indawo yokuphumla) yanaphakade
  75,13,"Umntu ngaloo Mini uya kuchazelwa ngoko wakhokelisa ngako (okuzizenzo) nawakunkonyayo, (akanikela ngako)"
  75,14,Ke kaloku umntu uya kuba lingqina (elaneleyo) ngokuchasene nesiqu sakhe
  75,15,Kanti nokuba sele ezithethelela
  75,16,"(Wena ke Muhammad) unganyakazisi ulwimi lwakho ngayo3 (i’Kur’ân), ungxame ngayo"
  75,17,InenekuxhomekekekuThiukuqokelelwakwayo(entliziyweni yakho) nokucengcelezwa kwayo
  75,18,Ke kaloku SiSakuyicengceleza (ngoJibrîl) wena landela ucengcelezo lwayo
  75,19,Kananjalo kukuThi ukucaciswa kwayo (kuwe)
  75,20,Nakanye! Nina (bantu) nithanda ukungxamela obu bomi
  75,21,Nibuyeke uBomi oBuzayo
  75,22,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kukhazimla
  75,23,Bejonge eNkosini yabo
  75,24,Ubuso babanye ngaloo Mini buya kumatsheka (buxwebe)
  75,25,Belindele ukuba baza kuhlelwa lilishwa phezu kwabo
  75,26,"Nakanye! Xa umphefumlo ufika kugovane, (kofayo)"
  75,27,"Kuye kuthiwe: “Ngubani na oza kumphilisa (amsindise ekufeni)?”"
  75,28,Ke kaloku yena (ofayo) uye aqonde okokuba (sele ilixesha lakhe) lokuhamba (kulo mhlaba)
  75,29,"Kananjalo\tomnye\tumlenze\tuye\tudityaniswe\tnomnye [wambathiswe ingubo yokufa (ikafan]"
  75,30,Ihambo ngaloo Mini ibhekisa eNkosini yakho (uAllâh)
  75,31,Ngoko ke ongakholwayo akazanga anikele (kumalizo) engazanga wathandaza nakuthandaza
  75,32,Kodwa endaweni yoko waphika watshikila
  75,33,Emva koko waya kubantu bakubo ehamba ngokuzingca (ngokuqhayisa)
  75,34,"Yeha kuwe (mntu ungakholwayo), yeha"
  75,35,"Kwakhona yeha kuwe mntu ungakholawayo, yeha"
  75,36,Umntu (lo) ucinga ukuba uza kuyekwa yedwa angahoywa na
  75,37,Wayengazanga waba liqabaza elivela kulwelo lwembewu yomntu na
  75,38,"Waza waba lihlwili elinamatheleyo, uAllâh Wadala isimo sakhe Wamlinganisela"
  75,39,"Wazangayewenzaabalinganeababini, oyindodanowasetyhini"
  75,40,Ingaba loo (Mdali) akakwazi ukunika bomi kwabafileyo na
  76,1,Ingaba akuzanga khe kubekho xesha na emntwini apho waye eyinto engafanelanga kukhankanywa na
  76,2,Inene Samdala UMntu ngomxube weqabaza lembewu yomntu khon’ukuze Simvavanye; kananjalo Samenzela ukuva nokubona
  76,3,"Samkhokela eNdleleni, nokuba uyabulela na okanye akabuleli"
  76,4,Kananjalo Silungiselele abangakholwayo amakhonkco namakhamandela neDangatya
  76,5,Inene wona amalungisa aya kusela indebe (yewayini) exutywe neKâfûr
  76,6,Umthombo ekuza kusela izicaka zika-Allâh ezingamalungisa (kwaye); ziwenza umpompoze ungaphezi
  76,7,Abo ke ngabo bazalisekisa izifungo zabo boyike neMini ekungcola kwayo kuya kuba banzi
  76,8,"Kananjalo bona bapha (abanye) ukutya nangona nabo bekuthanda (kodwa bakunike) abahlwempuzekileyo, noyinkedama, nongumthinjwa"
  76,9,"(Besithi): “Sinondlela ukukholisa uAllâh, asinqweneli mvuzo nambulelo kuni"
  76,10,"Inene thina soyika iMini enzima evela eNkosini yethu nephethe unxunguphalo, eya kwenza ubuso bubonakale busoyikeka.”"
  76,11,"Ngoko ke uAllâh uya kubasindisa bona ebubini baloo Mini, Abaphe ukukhanya kobuhle nolonwabo"
  76,12,"Kananjalo imbuyekezo yabo iya kuba yiPaladesi, nezambatho zesilika ngenxa yokuba kaloku bona baba nomonde"
  76,13,"(Bona baya kuba) behleli zava ezihlalweni zabo (ezimfuma- mfuma), abayi kubona langa nangqele apho"
  76,14,"Ngentla kufutshane nabo iya kuba yimithunzi yayo [iPaladesi (neziqhamo)] zayo ukuba bazinqothule, ziya kuthotyelwa ezantsi ukuba zivumele (ukunqothulwa)"
  76,15,Kananjalo kuya kuhanjiswa phakathi kwabo izitya neendebe eziya kuba zidalwe zacwenga
  76,16,Iigilasi ezicwengileyo ezenziwe ngesilivere ezimlinganiselo wazo wenziwe ngabo
  76,17,Kananjalo baya kunikwa indebe (yewayini) exutywe nejinja (ginger)
  76,18,"(Basele), kumthombo ophakathi (ePaladesi) obizwa ngokuba yiSalsabîl"
  76,19,Kuya kuba kuhamba-hamba amakhwenkwana enziwe ngonaphakade. Xa uwabona ungacinga ukuba aziiperile ezisarhaziweyo
  76,20,Naxa ujonga apho (ePaladesi) uya kubona ubumnandi nobungangamsha (bokwenene)
  76,21,"Baya kwambathiswa izambatho eziluhlaza zesilika esulungekileyo, engqindilili. Kananjalo baya kuhonjiswa ngezacholo zesilivere Ize iNkosi yabo Ibanike isiselo esihlambululayo"
  76,22,"(Kananjalo kuya kuthiwa): “Inene oku kuni ngumvuzo kananjalo, umzamo wenu uyabulelwa.”"
  76,23,"Inene SiThi Abathumele i’Kur’ân kuwe (Muhammad), amathuba ngamathuba"
  76,24,"Yiba nomonde ke ngesigqibo seNkosi yakho, ungathobeli (nawuphi na) umoni phakathi kwabo okanye ongenambulelo"
  76,25,Ke kaloku khumbula igama leNkosi yakho (emthandazweni) ekuseni nangokuhlwa
  76,26,Nasebusuku qubuda kuYo uYizukise ngobusuku (obo)
  76,27,"Inene abo [bangakholwayo (baleqa)], bathande ubomi balo mhlaba beshiya ngemva kwabo iMini ebuhlungu"
  76,28,"SiThi ababadalayo Sabomeleza izimo zabo, kanti Sithanda Singayijika imbonakalo yabo ngotshintsho (olwahluke) kwaphela"
  76,29,"Inene le Vesi (ye‘Kur’ân) isisiyalo, ngoko ke lowo uthandayo makazithabathele iNdlela eya eNkosini yakhe"
  76,30,"Ukanti nina aningekhe nikwazi, ngaphandle kokuba kuthande uAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguSolwazi nguSobulumko"
  76,31,Yena Uya kungenisa kwinceba yaKhe lowo Amthandileyo. Abenzi bobubi ke bona Ubalungiselele isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  77,1,(Ndifunga) ngemimoya ethunyelwa phambili omnye emva komnye
  77,2,Nangemimoya evuthuza ngamandla
  77,3,Nangemimoya echitha-chitha amafu nemvula
  77,4,NangeeVesi ze’Kur’ân ezahlula okulungileyo kokugwenxa
  77,5,Nangeengelosi ezizisa isiTyhilelo kubaProfeti
  77,6,Ukunqamla konke ukuzithethelela zilumkise nokulumkisa
  77,7,Inene oko nikuthenjisiweyo kunyanzelekile kwenzeke
  77,8,Xa iinkwenkwezi ziphelelwe kukukhanya kwazo
  77,9,Naxa izulu licandeka
  77,10,Naxa iintaba ziphaphatheke zemka
  77,11,"Naxa\tabaThunywa\tbehlanganiselwe\tixesha\tlabo elikhethiweyo"
  77,12,Yiyiphi le Mini le miqondiso irhoxiselwa yona
  77,13,(Irhoxiselwa) iMini yohlenga-hlengiso
  77,14,Yintoni na enokukwenza wazi ukuba iyintoni na iMini yohlengahlengiso
  77,15,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,16,ASizanga Sibatshabalalise na abamandulo
  77,17,Siya kwenza njalo ke nangezizukulwana zamva ukulandelisa
  77,18,Siqubisana kanjalo ke naboni
  77,19,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,20,ASizanga Sinidale ngolwelo olonyanyekayo na
  77,21,Saza Salubeka kwindawo yalo yokhuseleko (esibelekweni)
  77,22,Ixesha elingummiselo owaziwayo
  77,23,"Samisela ixesha elithile ngalo, (SiThi ke) abaMiseli xesha Abalungileyo"
  77,24,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,25,Asiwenzanga umhlaba waba sisiqulathi
  77,26,Sabaphilileyo nabaFileyo na
  77,27,Saza Sabeka apho kuwo iintaba ezinde eziqinileyo. Saninika amanzi amnandi ukuba nisele
  77,28,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,29,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yiyani koko nanidla ngokuphika"
  77,30,Yiyani ethunzini (lomsi woMlillo wesiHogo) oziingqimba ezintathu
  77,31,"(Kodwa) lingenamthunzi upholileyo, lingancedi nakunceda ngokuchasene neDangatya.”"
  77,32,"Inene\twona\tloo\t(msi)\tutakisa\tiintlantsi\t(ezinkulu) ezingangenqaba (yamajoni)"
  77,33,Ngathi ziinkamela ezilubhelu bumnyama
  77,34,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,35,Le yiMini abangayi kuthetha ngayo
  77,36,Bengayi kuvunyelwa nakuvunyelwa ukuba bazithethelele
  77,37,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,38,"Le\tyiMini\tyoMgwebo;\tSiya\tkuba\tSinihlanganisile nabamandulo"
  77,39,"Ukuba ngaba ninalo icebo, cebani kaloku ngokuchasene naM (ngoku)"
  77,40,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,41,"Inene\tabanyulu\tbaya\tkuba\tphakathi\tkwemithunzi nemithombo"
  77,42,Neziqhamo (zohlobo) abalufunayo
  77,43,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yidlani nisele nanele ngenxa yoko nakwenzayo.”"
  77,44,Inene Thina sibavuza kajalo ke abenzi bokulungileyo
  77,45,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,46,"(Hini na nina bangakholwayo), yibani nisitya nizonwabise okwethutyana inene nina ningaboni"
  77,47,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,48,"Ukanti xa kusithiwa kubo: Gobani amadolo (phambi koAllâh)”, abagobi bona"
  77,49,Yeha ngaloo Mini kubaphiki
  77,50,Yiyiphi ke enye intetho emva (kwe’Kur’ân) abaya kukholwa kuyo